## ğŸ“„ Step 5: Managing Invoices & Payments

### Viewing Invoices
1. Navigate to **Invoices**
2. View list of all invoices with status indicators
3. Click on any invoice to see details

### Processing a Payment
1. Open the invoice
2. Click **"Record Payment"**
3. Enter the payment amount
4. Select payment method
5. Submit the payment

### Applying Late Penalties
1. Open an overdue invoice
2. Click **"Apply Penalty"** for individual invoices
3. Or use **"Apply All Penalties"** for bulk processing

